6th Grade Family Dinner
In the spirit of connection for our SAAS community, please join us for grade level dinners this fall! This on campus evening event is a great
opportunity to meet and connect with other families in the same grade. Parents, students, and siblings are welcome. RSVP required.
Doors open at 6:00 PM with dinner starts at 6:30 PM
